Giessen, Universitätsbibliothek der Justus Liebig
Hs 1089. Magna carta with statutes; tracts; Natura brevium. 261 ff. 210 x 150 mm.
Provenance: Inscr. ‘Iste liber constat Johanni pulleyne de lyncolnes Inne’, fol. 1r; ‘Bibliothecae Academicae Publicae Senckenbergianae,’ ‘Bibl. Senk. C.20,’ i.e. Senkenburg, front pastedown.
